            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Network usage rules allow enterprises to specify how devices use networks, such as cellular data networks. iOS 9-12 require the application rules. In iOS 13, application rules, SIM rules, or both must be present.",
